|---|---|---|
| 🔴 P1 | Add authentication to `/users` | Medium |
| 🔴 P1 | Secure `.env` files / gitignore | Low |
| 🟠 P2 | Add `helmet` (security headers) | Low |
| 🟠 P2 | Add rate limiting | Low |
| 🟠 P2 | Configure CORS policy | Low |
| 🟠 P2 | Set body parser size limits | Low |
| 🟡 P3 | Add global error handler | Low |
| 🟡 P3 | Add input validation framework | Medium |
| 🟡 P3 | Add request logging | Low |
| 🟡 P3 | Minimize `/health` response | Low |
| 🟢 P4 | PII minimization in responses | Medium |
| 🟢 P4 | Graceful shutdown | Low |

